tux-im (0.1.0-2) resolute; urgency=medium

  * fix(config): _merge must read field TYPES, not values.  Use
    __dataclass_fields__[k].type instead of asdict() so the runtime
    type check in Config._apply does not crash on startup with
    "TypeError: isinstance() arg 2 must be a type, ...".

